Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.74,0:00:11.74,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{"Magic Users Fear For Their Lives:"}"Tính mạng của các pháp sư đang gặp nguy hiểm""
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.74,0:00:15.70,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{"Twenty Years After Defeat, \Nthe Infamous Antique Company Returns"?}Sau 20 năm bị đánh bại,\N Băng Đồ cổ tai tiếng đã trở lại"?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.70,0:00:19.46,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{The same Antique Company \Nthat's in }{\i1}{The Adventures of Nike}{\i0}{?}Giống với Băng Đồ cổ trong\N Những cuộc phiêu lưu của Nike sao?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.21,0:00:24.09,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Were they released from prison? \NOr is this the work of copycats?}Mãn hạn tù rồi sao? Hay là bắt chước thôi?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.09,0:00:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{By the way, have you heard what happened?}Này, bà nghe tin gì chưa?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's terrible.}Kinh khủng lắm.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.09,0:00:31.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{They say that awful Antique Company gang \Nis back and up to no good again.}Họ nói Băng Đồ cổ kinh khủng đó\N đã trở lại và gây hại như xưa.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.34,0:00:34.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{I thought they'd disappeared years ago!}Tưởng biến mất từ mấy năm trước rồi chứ!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.10,0:00:35.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's making me fear for my husband.}Không biết chồng tôi có sao không.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.97,0:00:38.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Do you think the attacks on \Nmagic users will start up again?}Liệu các pháp sư có lại bị tấn công không đây?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.48,0:00:39.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm so frightened.}Sợ quá.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.98,0:00:42.94,Elaina,,0,0,0,,Có vẻ không phải lúc để vui mừng rồi.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.94,0:00:45.65,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{I'd really like to avoid a hassle, too.}Cũng nên tránh xa rắc rối nữa.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.91,0:00:55.54,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Perfect! Nobody would possibly \Nmistake me for a magic user now!}Ngon! Giờ chẳng ai biết mình là pháp sư nữa!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.99,0:00:58.66,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{I'm just your average, ordinary peerless beauty!}Chỉ là một cô gái xinh đẹp bình thường vô hại thôi!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.66,0:01:01.71,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Now for some sightseeing!}Đi ngắm cảnh thôi nào!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.27,0:01:26.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Did you see that?}Thấy gì không?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.23,0:01:31.90,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{I'll head to the United Magic Association branch \Nstraight away and get this job over with.}Giờ cứ tới thẳng Hiệp hội Thống nhất Phép thuật\N rồi làm cho xong nào.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.90,0:01:36.20,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Nothing to it but to hand the chest over \Nand reap my reward. Couldn't be simpler!}Chỉ cần giao cái rương rồi nhận thưởng\N nên dễ như ăn cháo nhỉ.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.20,0:01:37.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{Look! That lady's a witch!}Phù thủy kìa!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.87,0:01:40.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{What could she be doing here?}Cô ấy làm gì ở đây vậy nhở?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.04,0:01:42.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{She couldn't have picked a worse time.}Đến lúc này thì tiêu rồi.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.08,0:01:45.38,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Is it my imagination, or are they all staring at me?}Là tưởng tượng hay là ai cũng lườm mình hết vậy?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.38,0:01:49.13,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Well, no wonder! I mean, look at me! I'm adorable!}Mà, mình dễ thương quá thì làm sao trách họ được nhể~
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.14,0:01:56.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{Abide a bit there, me lassie.}Cô bé ơi chờ chút nào.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.93,0:01:59.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hold on! I'm talking to ye!}Dừng lại! Tôi nói cô đấy!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.06,0:02:01.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{The lovely little witch lass up there.}Cô phù thủy dễ thương kia ơi~
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.85,0:02:04.65,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Oh? Well, you obviously must be talking about me!}Ủa? Chẳng lẽ bà đang nói chuyện với tôi á!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yes, right ye are.}Đúng rồi, cô đó.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.36,0:02:12.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{This town's a dangerous place \Nas of late, little witch lassie.}Thị trấn này dạo đây nguy hiểm lắm cô phù thủy ạ.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.40,0:02:17.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Some terrible harm may be lying in wait for ye, \Ngoing out in broad daylight dressed that way!}Đi đâu mà lại ăn mặc như vậy giữa ban ngày ban mặt, \Nkhông sợ tai ương ập tới sao?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.33,0:02:19.83,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Terrible harm?}Tai ương?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.83,0:02:22.12,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Has this town really gotten so dangerous?}Cái thị trấn này nguy hiểm đến vậy sao?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.12,0:02:25.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Aye, that it has! Ye'd quake from yer toes \Nto yer pointy hat to hear how bad it's got!}Nhìn từ chân đến chóp mũ là biết tệ đến mức nào rồi!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.50,0:02:29.00,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Even my hat, huh?}Hể? Cả cái mũ luôn á?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.05,Saya,,0,0,0,,{That sure does sound dangerous!}Nghe nguy hiểm phết!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.05,0:02:33.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{A youngster like ye may not know,}Một đứa nhóc như cô có khi chưa biết,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.09,0:02:37.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{but there was a time when many a \Nmagic user was waylaid by brigands here.}nhưng từng có lúc pháp sư bị làm gỏi\N bởi mấy tên cướp ở đây đấy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.14,0:02:41.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Each and every one of them \Nwent about shivering in fear!}Từng tên một đều rùng mình sợ hãi.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{Be quick about it!}Nhanh con mẹ nó lên!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.56,0:02:43.60,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hể?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.52,0:02:47.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh, nothing, nothing!}À, không có gì! hehe~
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.27,0:02:52.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Anyhow, in order to keep yourself safe in \Nthese parts, may I suggest you arm yourself with}Thế để giữ an toàn, tôi khuyên cô nên trang bị
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.28,0:02:58.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{one of the implements of personal protection we're \Noffering here at the Antiqu—I mean, the Curio Company?}một trong những vật phẩm tự vệ\N cung cấp bởi Băng Đồ c-- à nhầm Đồ lạ nhé?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.33,Saya,,0,0,0,,{I thought so!}Tôi cũng nghĩ vậy đó!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.66,0:03:05.29,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{I don't want any, so you can \Nstop with the sales pitch now!}Cơ mà chẳng cần thứ nào cả\N nên dừng chào mồi nữa nhá!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.29,0:03:07.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hold it!}Chờ cái đã!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.73,0:03:28.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry. I didn't get the chest from her.}Xin lỗi. \NEm chẳng lấy được cái rương.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.40,0:03:29.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{Tch!}Chặc!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.44,0:03:31.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{Still as useless a lunk as ever, are ye?}Vẫn vô dụng như mọi khi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.69,0:03:32.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{No matter.}Chẳng sao.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{Slight change of plan, that's all.}Thay đổi kế hoạch một chút thôi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.32,0:03:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{After all, we need only get that chest open.}Dù gì chỉ cần mở cái rương đó ra là được nhỉ.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.38,0:03:57.43,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Shouldn't the branch office \Nbe somewhere around here?}Chi nhánh Hội phải ở quanh đây nhỉ?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.19,0:04:15.28,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Not good! Is this curtains for me?}Tiêu rồi! Mình sẽ bỏ mạng ở đây sao?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.28,0:04:18.24,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Keep your voice down. \NThis town is a very dangerous place.}Nói nhỏ thôi.\N Thị trấn này nguy hiểm lắm.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.21,0:04:34.50,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Mina? Wow, long time no see!}Mina? Lâu rồi không gặp!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.80,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Uh, so what brings my little sister here?}Ủa? Làn gió nào đưa em gái chị tới đây?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.14,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{The Association sent me here \Non an undercover mission.}Hội gửi em tới đây để làm nhiệm vụ ngầm.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.93,0:04:48.56,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{It looks like a local gang of ruffians \Nis plotting something nefarious.}Có vẻ mấy tên cướp ở đây\N đánh hơi được thứ gì bất chính rồi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.56,0:04:50.60,Saya,,0,0,0,,{I haven't managed to infiltrate them yet.}Em vẫn chưa thâm nhập vào được.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.10,Saya,,0,0,0,,{What sort of something nefarious?}Thứ gì bất chính cơ?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.86,0:04:55.02,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{How about you? What are you doing here?}Tại sao chị lại ở đây?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.86,Saya,,0,0,0,,{I'm here for work, same as you.}Chị cũng làm việc, như em thui.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.11,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Association business!}Công việc của Hội!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.78,0:05:03.03,Saya,,0,0,0,,Việc của Hội vào giữa lúc này?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.08,Saya,,0,0,0,,{I came to deliver this.}Để giao thứ này nè.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.20,Saya,,0,0,0,,{What is it?}Cái gì đây?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.08,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Beats me.}Chả biết.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.58,0:05:10.16,Saya,,0,0,0,,Nhưng em có nghe gì từ bên Hội đâu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.13,0:05:22.18,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{For the time being, come with me \Nto the room where I'm staying.}Giờ trước hết thì cứ đi với em về nơi em đang ở đã.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.18,0:05:26.18,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Oh, I really should deliver this first, plus I'd hate to \Nimpose on you, so I'll get my own room in the inn.}À, chị nên giao cái này trước hơn nữa\N chị không muốn ở nhờ nên sẽ thuê phòng khác ở trọ.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.68,Saya,,0,0,0,,{No need to worry about me!}Đừng có lo cho chị!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.81,0:05:29.43,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Oh?}Thế à?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.35,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Every time you heave a sigh, \Naway from you does fortune fly!}Mỗi khi thở dài là may mắn bay hết đấy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.67,0:05:57.13,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{I know that tearoom!}Mình biết phòng trà này!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.13,0:06:01.09,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{That has to be where Fura confronted \Nthe Antique Company boss!}Đây hẳn là nơi Fura đối đầu\N với bang chủ Băng Đồ cổ mà!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.51,0:06:05.30,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Wow!}Quao~
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.10,0:06:09.31,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{I wonder which of these tables \Nis the one where Fura sat?}Không biết Fura ngồi bàn nào nhỉ?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.18,0:06:12.27,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Wow!}Quao~
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{She'll do right nicely.}Con đó nhìn ngon ăn đấy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.98,0:06:16.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{Are you sure?}Chắc chứ ạ?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{She seems like a right twit.}Nhìn mặt nó ngu vậy mà.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.36,0:06:23.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Just the sort who'll open up that chest \Nwith nary a second thought.}Chắc chắn là người sẽ mở rương\N mà chẳng nghĩ ngợi gì cả.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.67,0:06:42.76,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Are you listening?}Nghe chứ?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.76,0:06:44.68,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Don't try and do anything, Sister.}Chị đừng cố làm gì cả.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.68,0:06:47.39,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Sister?}Chị? Ai cơ?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.39,0:06:48.43,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Where am I?}Đây là đâu?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.43,0:06:50.85,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Wasn't I standing in front of the tearoom just now?}Mới nãy đứng ở phòng trà kia mà?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.85,0:07:00.27,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{They're planning to rob every jeweller, weaponsmith, \Nand any other store in town they can.}Bọn chúng đang lên kế hoạch trộm hết tiệm đá quý,\N vũ khí cùng các thứ li ti trong thị trấn.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.44,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is this... a dream?}Mơ sao?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.44,0:07:03.03,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Guess not.}Không phải.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{Sister, are you listening to me?}Chị nghe em nói chứ?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.86,0:07:08.57,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Excuse me, but who are you?}Xin lỗi, em là ai vậy?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.12,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{See, I'm...}Tôi...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.12,0:07:14.96,Saya,,0,0,0,,{This isn't the time to joke around.}Đây không phải lúc đùa giỡn nên thế nào cũng được.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.54,0:07:17.21,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{I wasn't joking...}Dù không đùa...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.21,0:07:19.46,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{and what happened to my voice?}nhưng giọng mình bị sao vậy nè?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.09,0:07:21.92,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{What?}Ủa?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.22,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Sister?}Chị?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.36,0:07:41.77,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Sister, what are you doi—}Chị? Chị làm gì--
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.67,0:08:02.38,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What is this? Poisonous gas?}Gì đây? Khí độc à?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.31,0:08:27.45,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{I was so stunned at this sudden meeting \Nwith my destiny that I forgot to breathe!}Choáng váng vì đột nhiên gặp định mệnh\N làm quên mất cả thở luôn!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.62,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Miss Elaina!}Chị Elaina!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.79,0:08:44.09,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Hey, are you all right?}Này, em có sao không?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.30,0:08:49.84,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Sis...ter?}Chị?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.43,0:08:54.01,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Are you feeling sick?}Bị đau ở đâu sao?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.22,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Is it your stomach?}Đau bụng à?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.35,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Or a fever?}Hay cảm?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.35,0:08:58.23,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Do you feel nauseous?}Thấy buồn nôn không?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.23,0:09:01.31,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Don't touch me!}Đừng có chạm vào em!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.69,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Ouch!}Đau!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.57,0:09:07.90,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{U-Um...}Hả...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.57,0:09:10.07,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Sister...}Chị này...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.58,0:09:16.37,Saya,,0,0,0,,{You're so adorable...}Dễ thương quá...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.91,0:09:20.08,Saya,,0,0,0,,{I love you!}Yêu chị!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.46,0:09:24.46,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Oh, my dear sister, I've loved you for so long!}Chị yêu dấu! Em đã luôn luôn yêu chị!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.05,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Do you think that's strange?}Có lạ quá không?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.30,0:09:30.05,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{But for ages and ages, \Nyou've been the only thing I think about!}Từ rất lâu rồi, chị là người duy nhất em nghĩ đến!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.05,0:09:34.01,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Even though you're the older one, \Nyou follow me around like a little puppy.}Dù là chị lớn nhưng chị lúc nào\N cũng theo em như một con cún vậy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.01,0:09:37.64,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{You're so pathetic, and totally reliant on your \Nlittle sister, and that's what makes you so adorable!}Chị thật thảm hại, toàn dựa dẫm vào em gái\N nhưng nó thật là dễ thương!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.64,0:09:38.85,Saya,,0,0,0,,{You're so cute I can't stand it!}Mồ, thực sự...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.85,0:09:45.40,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{You're so cute, so so cute, so so so cute, \Nso so so so }{\i1}{so}{\i0}{ cute that it's more than I can bear!}dễ thương quá, dễ thương quá, dễ thương,\N dễ thương không chịu nổi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.40,0:09:49.90,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Ahh! You're all I need, my dear, dear sister!}Mồ! Chị là tất cả những gì mà em cần, chị yêu dấu!!!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.49,0:09:54.41,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Yet I always treat you so coldly! I'm so sorry!}Thế mà lúc nào em cũng lạnh nhạt! \NXin lỗi nhé!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.74,0:10:00.16,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Sorry that I never made my true feelings known \Nuntil now, though I love you so deeply!}Xin lỗi vì chưa từng thổ lộ em yêu chị\N sâu đậm tới nhường nào!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.16,0:10:06.46,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{I love you so, so, so, so, so, so, \Nso very much that I could just eat you up!}Em thực sự muốn ăn tươi chị luôn,\N em yêu yêu yêu yêu chị!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.46,0:10:10.51,Saya,,0,0,0,,{I really love you so, so, so, so, so, }{\i1}{so}{\i0}{ much!}Yêu yêu yêu yêu yêu nhiều lém!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.51,0:10:11.92,Saya,,0,0,0,,{So please, dear sister,}Nên là, xin chị,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.51,Saya,,0,0,0,,{can't you and I—}chị với em---
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.34,0:10:15.43,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{No!}No!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.52,0:10:21.43,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Ooh...}Ẹc...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.57,0:10:32.95,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Do I even }{\i1}{want}{\i0}{ to know what's going on here?}Mồ! Thực sự chẳng biết cái gì nữa?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{What are you doing?}Làm gì đấy?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.41,0:10:36.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey, hold on a second!}Chờ chút đã!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.45,0:10:39.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{Wait for me!}Chờ tui với!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.33,Main,,900,0,0,,{Stay away!}Né ra!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{Get a hold of yourself!}Bình tĩnh đi!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{So long have I loved you!}Anh đã yêu em từ lâu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.37,Main,,0,900,0,,{But I'm in love with your brother!}Nhưng tui yêu anh trai của em!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.79,0:10:45.37,Main,,1200,0,0,,{I love you!}Yêu lắm nhé!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.37,0:10:47.42,Main,,0,900,0,,{I appreciate the sentiment, but no thanks!}Tui cảm kích lắm \Nnhưng cảm ơn xin kiếu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.96,0:10:47.42,Main,,900,0,0,,{Ah, how I love you!}Yêu!!!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.34,0:10:50.38,Main,,0,900,0,,{What happened to you? You're freaking me out!}Bị sao vậy? Thấy gớm quá!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.38,Main,,900,0,0,,{Wait up!}Chờ đã!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.59,0:10:58.22,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{This is a mite unusual.}Chuyện này Crazy~ thật nhỉ.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.22,0:11:02.60,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{And it's probably... no, definitely \Nhappening because I opened that chest.}Hình như... không, là chắc chắn do mình mở cái rương.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.60,0:11:05.60,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Ahh! I love you!}Ahhh! Yêu quá!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.02,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Isn't that voice...}Cái giọng đó...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{No!}Không!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.15,0:11:11.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{Don't be afraid of my love!}Đừng ngại mà!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.15,0:11:17.11,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{I'm so cute! Every single part \Nof me is simply the cutest!}Quả là dễ thương mà! Nhìn đâu cũng dễ thương hết!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.62,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Th-That's definitely...}A-Đó chắn chắn là...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.62,0:11:22.08,Saya,,0,0,0,,{I wub yoo!}Iu nhém!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.37,0:11:24.79,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{No mistaking it—that would be me.}Không nhầm được-- Đó là mình mà.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.13,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{...Saya?}...Saya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.13,0:11:32.05,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hể?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.26,0:11:34.59,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{...Me?}...Mình?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.02,0:11:45.48,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What?}{\i0}{ What are you talking about?}Hả? Thế là sao hả?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.90,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{I have no idea what's going on here!}Chị chả hiểu chuyện gì đang xảy ra ở đây cả!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.94,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{I demand an explanation for this, Saya!}Chị yêu cầu một lời giải thích, Saya!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.94,0:11:52.44,Saya,,0,0,0,,{I don't know any more than you do!}Em cũng có biết tí gì đâu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.44,0:11:56.32,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{All I know is that when I came to, I found myself \Nin the adorable form of you, Miss Elaina!}Em chỉ biết khi mở mắt ra, em đã ở trong\N hình hài dễ thương của chị Elaina rồi!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.32,0:12:01.41,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{I have no idea what made all \Nthe townspeople go crazy, either!}Còn tại sao người dân phát điên\N thì em cũng chả biết luôn!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.91,0:12:04.24,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Oh, that doesn't really concern me.}À, cái đó thì ra sao cũng được.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.08,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{I know what caused it.}Chị biết nguyên nhân rồi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.08,0:12:06.66,Saya,,0,0,0,,{What?!}Hả?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.42,0:12:11.63,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Anyway, as to why we've switched bodies...}Thế, tại sao ta lại đổi cơ thể với nhau...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.63,0:12:15.59,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Wait, back up. You know what caused \Nthis to happen to the townspeople?}Mà, sao chị biết nguyên nhân vậy?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.47,0:12:19.09,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Let's put that aside for now.}Chuyện đó bỏ qua một bên đi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.51,0:12:23.85,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{I should have had a chest with me.\N What happened to it?}Em có mang theo cái rương...\N...ủa, giờ nó đâu rồi?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.39,0:12:27.94,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Apparently it was some super dangerous \Nartefact I wasn't supposed to open, ever.}Nó là thứ cực kì nguy hiểm\N mà em không được mở ra đấy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.94,Main,,0,900,0,,{Wait for me!}Chờ tui!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.90,0:12:32.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{Here I am!}Đến đây!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.52,0:12:35.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{You scamp! Wait up!}Con đũy! Chờ đã!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.86,0:12:40.20,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Don't tell me... you opened it?}Đừng nói là... chị mở nó ra rồi?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.20,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Well...}Thì...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.37,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Just a teeny little bit.}Chỉ chút thui.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.37,0:12:48.37,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Oh, for heaven's sake! What were you thinking?!}Trời má! Chị nghĩ cái gì vậy hả?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.42,0:12:53.25,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Clearly something terrible \Nwas going to happen if you did!}Nhìn là biết sẽ có thứ gì nguy hiểm xảy ra mà!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.80,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Why didn't my sister stop you?}Sao em gái em không ngăn chị hả?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.80,0:12:56.96,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Your sister?}Em gái?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.34,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Haven't you seen her?}Chị chưa gặp sao?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.63,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{A girl with long black hair and \Na strangely erotic air to her?}Một cô gái với mái tóc dài\N với chút quyễn rũ lạ thường.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.93,0:13:03.51,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Ahh... yeah, she was there.}À... có ở đó.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.18,Saya,,0,0,0,,{You've got dead fish eyes.}Mắt nhìn như chết thế.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.81,0:13:11.81,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Pretty strong family resemblance you two have.}Hai đứa quả là người nhà nhỉ.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.61,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Oh? Do you really think so?}Ể? Chị nghĩ thế sao?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.61,0:13:15.11,Saya,,0,0,0,,{You're pulling my leg!}Đừng có khen em thế mà!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.82,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Please stop. I don't want to see that \Ndrippy expression on my own face.}Làm ơn dừng lại. Chị không muốn thấy\N cái vẻ tự luyến ấy trên mặt mình đâu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.20,0:13:24.53,Saya,,0,0,0,,{What? What expression?}Gì? Cái vẻ gì cơ?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.87,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Ooh! I just love you!}A! Yêu quá đi!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.75,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Would you get away from that window?}Tránh xa cái cửa sổ đó ra.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.75,0:13:36.50,Saya,,0,0,0,,{No way! I'll never be away from you again, Miss Elaina!}Không muốn! \NEm không muốn phải xa chị Elaina một lần nào nữa!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.50,0:13:42.47,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Our first priority should be \Nputting the town back to normal.}Giờ ưu tiên hàng đầu là biến thị trấn\N trở lại như cũ đấy nhé.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.47,0:13:46.76,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Actually, I guess I should say }{\i1}{my}{\i0}{ first priority.}Không, thực ra là ưu tiên hàng đầu của mình.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.97,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{I'm the reason things ended up like this.}Mình là người gây ra chuyện này.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.97,0:13:54.81,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Well, since I'm you right now, \NI should do the same thing, right?}Vậy, giờ em là chị Elaina rồi, em làm \Ngiống chị được chứ nhỉ?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.81,0:13:57.90,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{I appreciate the thought, but I'd rather \Njust have you get away from that window.}Chị biết ơn lắm nhưng\N chị chỉ cần em buông tha cái cửa sổ ra.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.90,0:14:01.49,Saya,,0,0,0,,{But what do you suppose was inside that chest?}Nhưng chị biết có thứ gì trong cái rương chưa? Mlem~ mlem~
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.74,0:14:03.99,Elaina,,0,0,0,,Cái này gọi là lời nguyền thì đúng hơn là phép thuật.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.99,0:14:06.49,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Something like a love potion, I suppose.}Thứ gì đó như tình dược chăng.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Wait up, you big silly!}Chờ đã, đồ ngốc~
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.49,0:14:11.08,Saya,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Do you think they switched us \Nand then had you open the chest?}Có khi nào chúng đổi em với chị\N để chị mở cái rương không?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Hee hee hee!}He he he!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.58,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{Who would rely on such a sloppy plan?}Ai lại nghĩ ra cái kế hoạch cẩu thả này nhỉ?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.58,0:14:17.50,Saya,,0,0,0,,{You have a point. That's way too sloppy to be realistic.}Đúng vậy nhỉ. \NNó thực sự cẩu thả so với thực tế.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{Everything went according to the boss's plan!}Mọi thứ đều diễn ra theo kế hoạch của bang chủ!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.05,0:14:27.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{The United Magic Association totally bought that \Nfake request, and those dumb witches waltzed right in}Hiệp hội Thống nhất Phép thuật nhận yêu cầu giả\N rồi đám phù thủy ngu ngốc dính bẫy ngay.
