Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.92,Saya,,0,0,0,,{Could those ruffians be...}Có khi nào đám cướp đó là...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.34,Elaina,,0,0,0,,{The Antique Company has returned, huh?}Băng Đồ cổ đã trở lại hả?
